Class ResultsExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codeavengers.main.data.db.AbstractExtractor<Results>
      • org.codeavengers.main.data.db.extractor.ResultsExtractor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.jdbc.core.ResultSetExtractor<Results>

    public class ResultsExtractor
extends AbstractExtractor<Results>
    This is a generic implementation of ResultSetExtractor which allows capturing any database query output in generic java beans. A combination of the Result and Results entities are leveraged to achieve a generic mapping.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    abhishek
